msgid "Units unlock permanently"
msgstr "Desbloqueo de unidades permanente"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/name"
msgid "Kharkov"
msgstr "Járkov"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/name_big"
msgid "Kharkov"
msgstr "Járkov"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/story"
msgid "The third battle of Kharkov - Counterattack. We have to re-take Kharkov. Failure would result in a big gap in the front line.\n\nGoals:\n - Take the town in a swift counterattack.\n - Destroy all abandoned enemy material."
msgstr ""
"La tercera batalla de Járkov;\n"
"Contraataque# Tenemos que retomar Járkov.\n"
"\n"
"El fracaso resultaría en una gran brecha en la línea del frente.\n"
"\n"
"Objetivos:\n"
" - Tomar la ciudad en un rápido contraataque.\n"
" - Destruir todo el material enemigo abandonado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/place"
msgid "On the west side of Kharkov"
msgstr "En el lado oeste de Járkov"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/date"
msgid "February, 1943"
msgstr "Febrero de 1943"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/outro_start"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Congratulations! Your counterattack was executed brilliantly. The frontline "
"is closed once again! We lost an appalling number of men today, and we owe "
"it to them to hold Kharkov at any cost."
msgstr ""
"¡Felicidades! Su contraataque fue ejecutado brillantemente. ¡La línea del "
"frente está cerrada una vez más! Perdimos un número espantoso de hombres "
"hoy, y les debemos el mantener Járkov a cualquier precio."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This was a failure, maybe not surprising - considering the enemy has enjoyed "
"overwhelming numerical superiority. Whatever is left of your troops will now "
"retreat in chaos with the red army in hot pursuit."
msgstr ""
"Ha sido un fracaso, quizá no sorprendente, teniendo en cuenta que el enemigo "
"ha disfrutado de una abrumadora superioridad numérica. Lo que queda de sus "
"tropas ahora se retirará en el caos con el ejército rojo en la persecución "
"caliente."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/outro_failed_hq"
msgid "Mission failed - the enemy captured your HQ!"
msgstr "¡Misión fallida! - ¡El enemigo ha capturado tu cuartel general!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/mission_hq"
msgid "You must hold your field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Debes mantener tu cuartel general de campo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/mission_attack"
msgid "Capture the outskirts of Kharkov!"
msgstr "¡Capturen las afueras de Járkov!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/flag_capture_status"
msgid "Your soldiers secured %1%/7 Soviet positions!"
msgstr "¡Tus soldados aseguraron el %1%/7 de las posiciones soviéticas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/narrator_start0"
msgid ""
"Welcome to battle, Major! This is our field HQ, it must remain in our "
"control!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido a la batalla, Mayor! Este es nuestro cuartel general de campo, "
"¡debe permanecer bajo nuestro control!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/narrator_start1"
msgid ""
"You need to attack at full speed! Use the mobility of your armor to achieve "
"surprise."
msgstr ""
"Tienes que atacar a toda velocidad. Utiliza la movilidad de tu armadura para "
"lograr la sorpresa."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/narrator_start2"
msgid ""
"The soviets deployed many tanks. Make sure you spot them before rushing in!"
msgstr ""
"Los soviéticos desplegaron muchos tanques. ¡Asegúrate de localizarlos antes "
"de entrar a toda prisa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/narrator_start3"
msgid ""
"Begin securing the objectives, meanwhile more reinforcements are being "
"prepared for deployment!"
msgstr ""
"Comiencen a asegurar los objetivos, ¡mientras se preparan más refuerzos para "
"su despliegue!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Comrades! Soviets are close to our Field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Camaradas! ¡Los soviéticos están cerca de nuestro cuartel general!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "We must hold the command post! There can be no surrender!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos mantener el puesto de mando! ¡No se puede hablar de retirada aquí!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1943_02-ger_kharkov/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request an airstrike, ZG 1 is at your disposal."
msgstr ""
"¡Mayor! Ahora puede solicitar un ataque aéreo, ZG 1 está a su disposición."
